{"tid":1439523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老啟發] 巴士文宣！民間Roadshow!","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:52:41.000Z","uid":73507,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"37b870593984daadb0cb7b472d1d51ccd58fa253","tid":1439523,"uid":73507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"成日搭巴士都會聽到d 廢老播片播到勁大聲，但d 人寧願耳仔受罪都無話佢，聽足成程車，我地都可以反其道而行！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵依家都會播新聞，但因為人多嘈收音差同通常好快轉車，好難專心留意發生咩事。Airdrop 又唔係每個人都用Apple，加上唔想收既人一早都turn off 左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭巴士大家有時間坐定定，呢個係一個機會去做文宣。可唔可以好似之前遊行見到個播片巴咁，整番民間流動road show。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係巴士播片播聲，不論係警察，林鄭記者會重點，定係警察濫捕濫權既片段，襯大家坐定定既時候播，要大家接收 因為依家覺得亂而拒絕接收既事實！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af269e53003e9bf2fb491b6d7c91656220ef1de","tid":1439523,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">推行動post呀<br />\n推上熱門呀<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"54f6ded41ecf3cb2483d53acbd36102577125786","tid":1439523,"uid":229553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"入嚟投票啊<br />\nGoogle Form:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/DypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68syKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=b0db8158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNxu1GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj