 試過屌鳩人係巴士播撐警集會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"明白既所以先會話係受佢地啟發，係會有人白眼，但唔係個個都會出聲，變左被逼接收。<br />\n<br />\n呢個諗發係針對只會被動接收訊息既人，或者播記者會官方d, 無咁偏頗會引起人好奇呢。有時樓下等lift 播新聞都會望多兩眼，甚至會睇到唔小心skip 左一程。"},{"pid":"6ff99d02fee16d4ac40e9e955cbc12c9a8b148eb","tid":1439523,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"光復福建！時代革命！福建獨立！"},{"pid":"53d14ab44612eeddb34c0726f8f5c86824e33599","tid":1439523,"uid":73507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"212ce0f59837328d9e97b28e44c689a789bb662a","tid":1439523,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"巴士我覺得你印文宣痴落座位後面廣告位仲好<br />\n你又騷擾唔到其他人<br />\n唔會有爭執<br />\n傳播度又高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"都可以喎，可以考慮易撕既貼紙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4248472579ad3b67f255122c7c89497980dc374a","tid":1439523,"uid":73507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40b7eddf7d5c8a9c933c242ab8e746de76f01db","tid":1439523,"uid":73507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff15017900185ad44d4303de4f7a3f4c59be6c07","tid":1439523,"uid":73507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2d3114533e05d3edeb7056b33db7fef3a6311d","tid":1439523,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike"